flowRoot.flowPara: We have strong team of Drupal & Symfony developers which can bring your ideas to life!
We have HR managers who will build development team fit your needs!

Skilld is a French open-source company with talented web project managers and high prospects. We are working with key account customers (typically biggest #100 French companies or big communication agencies : McDonald's, Pernod-Ricard, EDF, Hachette, Dunod, Uniball, Posca, Talika, TBWA, DDB, Rapp, ...) on complex web / mobile projects which usually involve about 3 or 10 people during a few months (3 to 12 months).

Recently, Skilld has made a quality breakthrough. Due to fast development, the company became requiring Drupal developers and designers also. They required full-time employees for remote work with projects from France.
There are asked requirements to the newcomers of the company:
original approach to solving of tasks;
pivotal knowledge of the English language;
responsibility towards work (crucial point of the remote staff selection).
We had selected dozens of specialist for advanced interview; after it, we chose four high-grade developers and a designer.
After several years of cooperating, We may confidently say that Skilld is a great customer and excellent partner.
